<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tech Studio Student Docket</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: "Open
      Sans", system-ui, sans-serif; } body { display: grid; /* grid-row: 1fr; */
      justify-content: center; align-items: center; /* height: 100vh; */ width:
      100%; } .container { background-color: #fafafa; width: 60rem; margin: 0
      auto; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 0 2px #5a5a5a; margin-block:
      2rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div style="padding: 2rem; padding-block: 3rem">
        <div
          style="
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
          "
        >
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto auto">
            <div style="color: #5a5a5a; gap: 6px">
              <p style="color: #1f2666; font-size: 1.3rem">
                TechStudio Academy
              </p>
              <p style="max-width: 22rem">
                1, Ogunlesi Street, Off Bode Thomas, Awoyokun Bus Stop, Onipanu,
                Lagos State.
              </p>
              <p style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2px">
                <img
                  src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgde8cwjk/image/upload/v1710404776/email%20template/call_xe3nsv.png"
                  alt=""
                />
                +2348109712678, +2348113800161, +2348126051769.
              </p>
              <div style="display: flex; gap: 5px">
                <p style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2px">
                  <img
                    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgde8cwjk/image/upload/v1710404777/email%20template/sms_xvgebp.png"
                    alt=""
                  />
                  info@techstudioacademy.com
                </p>
                <p style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2px">
                  <img
                    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgde8cwjk/image/upload/v1710404776/email%20template/chrome_cu9tjz.png"
                    alt=""
                  />
                  www.techstudioacademy.com
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <img
              style="padding-left: 210px"
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dgde8cwjk/image/upload/v1710404777/email%20template/Frame_1000003521_hrbtah.png"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <div
              style="
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                margin-block: 30px;
              "
            >
              <p
                class=""
                style="
                  text-align: center;
                  color: #fafafa;
                  background-color: #1f2666;
                  padding-block: 0.4rem;
                  width: 19rem;
                  border-radius: 6px;
                "
              >
                STUDENT ENROLLMENT DOCKET
              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              style="
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
                width: 100%;
                gap: 2rem;
              "
            >
              <div
                style="
                  display: flex;
                  flex-direction: column;
                  width: 100%;
                  gap: 22px;
                "
              >
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 4rem; width: 100%">
                  <table style="width: 100%">
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Full Name
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666">{{name}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Popularly Known As
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666">{{pka}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Student ID
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666">{{studentId}}</p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Email Address
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666">{{email}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Phone Number
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666">{{phoneNumber}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Course Cohort
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666; font-size: 15px">
                            {{courseCohort}}
                          </p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Course Duration
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666"></p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Course Type
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #1f2666">{{classType}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p
                            style="
                              color: #5a5a5a;
                              font-size: 12px;
                              line-height: 2;
                            "
                          >
                            Valid Till
                          </p>
                          <p style="color: #e00017"></p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                  <img style="max-width: 30%" src={{image}} alt="" />
                </div>
                <div
                  style="
                    margin-block: 26px;
                    text-align: center;
                    color: #747474;
                    font-size: 13px;
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    gap: 25px;
                    align-items: center;
                    width: 33rem;
                    margin-inline: auto;
                  "
                >
                  <p style="color: #747474; font-size: 16px">
                    IMPORTANT INFORMATION
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Please note the following as they guide the usage of the
                    enrollment docket.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                    Nihil autem eos, facilis aut blanditiis consequatur et optio
                    obcaecati excepturi dicta illum iste ea velit, Lorem ipsum
                    dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing eli
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>